                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Sleeper</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-08-29">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">August</hi> 29, 1906</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Sleeper reports that Asbert, the rebel leader, Habana Province, is quoted in
                    La Discussion as threatening to burn foreign properties after 15th proximo,
                    unless Government grants demands of revolutionists.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
